Package: dnssec-publish-ds
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser, init-system-helpers (>= 1.54~)
Static-Built-Using: ${misc:Static-Built-Using}
Suggests: bash-completion
Description: DNSSEC DS record publisher daemon
 Monitors CDS/CDNSKEY records for configured DNS zones and automatically
 updates DS records at the registrar via provider plugins.
 .
 Currently supports OVH API v1 as a provider.

Package: xymon-ext-dnssec
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, perl, hobbit-plugins, libnet-dns-perl, libnet-dns-sec-perl, libyaml-tiny-perl
Recommends: xymon
Description: Xymon server extension for DNSSEC zone checks
 Perl probe for Xymon server ext to validate DNSSEC chain health for zones.
 It verifies parent DS to zone DNSKEY consistency, signature validity windows,
 NSEC3 recommendation, and CDS/CDNSKEY presence policy.
